title: Show Mission Pass
description:
Earn even more rewards from Show
 Missions by purchasing a Premium Mission Pass.

title: VIRTUAL SINGERS in other SEKAI?
description:
Miku and her friends dress differently in each SEKAI, and
 help each character find their true feelings.

title: How are SEKAI created?
description: SEKAI are born of someone's true feelings.

title: Untitled?
description:
Untitled songs are linked to their SEKAI.
 They have neither melody nor lyrics.

title: Practice Scores - How to Obtain & Use ①
description:
Go to Practice to level up
 your characters.

title: Music Cards - How to Obtain & Use
description: Get new songs at the Music Shop.

title: Music Cards - How to Obtain & Use
description:
Obtain Music Cards by progressing the
 story or clearing missions.

title: Miracle Gems - How to Obtain & Use
description:
3★ and higher characters can be Upgraded
 to increase their stats and level cap.

title: Costume Materials - How to Obtain & Use
description:
Visit the Costume Shop in the
 Shopping Mall to make Costumes.

title: You can use between 0 and 5 Bonus Energy.
description:
You can use a maximum of 5 Bonus Energy.
 This amount increases to 10 during events.

title: You can use between 0 and 5 Bonus Energy.
description: Bonus Energy restores at a rate of 1 every 30 minutes.

title: Game settings can be changed from the Options screen.
description:
Note Speed can be changed from
 the options at any time.

title: Check a character's Profile to see their Info.
description:
You can view a character's introduction
 from their profile.

title: Miku Display in Deck
description:
The Miku displayed in 3D Music Videos
 can be set from the Costumes screen.

title: Obtaining Avatar Costumes
description:
Purchase costumes for your Virtual Show
 avatar at the Virtual Show in the Lobby.

title: Obtaining Virtual Coins
description:
Earn Virtual Coins from login bonuses
 and various events.

title: Virtual Show Rewards
description:
Virtual Shows are held on special occasions
 such as birthdays or after events.

title: Virtual Show Rewards
description:
Earn Crystals by viewing a
 Virtual Show for the first time.

title: Changing Costumes
description:
Costumes worn by characters during shows
 can be changed from the Costume menu.

title: Skill Activation in Solo Shows
description:
In Solo Shows, each member's skill activates
 once. The Leader's will activate twice.

title: Skill Activation in Co-op Shows ①
description:
In Co-op Shows, the player performing
 the best (ON FIRE) will activate their skill last.

title: Fan Pts - Acquisition & Use
description:
Using Virtual Items will earn you Fan Pts
 as well as Wish Pieces after a show.

title: MVP and SUPERSTAR
description:
Players who earn a high enough score
 in a Co-op Show will be crowned a SUPERSTAR.

title: Being ON FIRE in a Co-op Show
description:
Perform well (ON FIRE) in a Co-op Show by getting
 combos to give a score bonus to all players.

title: View Card Episodes to Boost Stats
description:
Viewing member's Side Stories
 will increase their Talent.

title: Playing Challenge Shows
description:
Earn Crystals and Character EXP by
 increasing Challenge Show's Stages.

title: Playing Challenge Shows
description:
Surpass certain high scores in a
 Challenge Show to earn Crystals.

title: Decorations - Basic Effects
description:
Decorations can boost the Talent
 of members and Groups.

title: Decorations - Basic Effects
description:
Once you own a Decoration, its
 effect will be applied automatically.

title: Unlock Costume Patterns by Getting 4★ Characters
description:
Obtain a 4★ character that comes with
 a costume to receive that costume and unlock it in the Costume Shop.

title: Wishes - Acquisition & Use
description:
Wish Jewels and Wish Pieces are
 required for Mastery and Skill Up.

title: Wishes - Acquisition & Use
description:
Receive Wish Jewels by trading
 4★ characters in the Green Room.

title: Wishes - Acquisition & Use
description: Receive Wish Pieces by trading 3★, 2★ or Birthday Characters in the Green Room.

title: Virtual Show Avatar Appearance
description:
Go to Virtual Show Avatar to change
 your Avatar's color and appearance.

title: Increasing Character Rank
description:
You can earn special rewards by
 increasing the Character Rank of your members.

title: Increasing Character Rank
description:
Characters will receive boosts to their
 Talent based on their Character Rank.

title: Increasing Character Rank
description:
Earn Character Rank EXP by completing
 Challenge Shows and character missions.

title: Earning Titles
description:
Titles can be earned by
 completing various missions.

title: Earning Titles
description:
Effects from titles which boost Talent
 are always active, even when not equipped.

title: Show Mission Points Reset
description:
Show Missions reset at 00:00 PST
on the 1st day of every month.

title: View Area Bonus Details from the Items Menu
description:
Effects of Decorations owned
 can be confirmed from the Items screen.

title: Decorations - Leveling & Advantages
description:
Charms, Gems, and Magical Seeds
 are required to level up Decorations.

title: Unlocking Challenge Show Slots
description:
The number of member slots available in Challenge
 Shows is determined by a character's Character Rank.

title: Increase Mastery Rank to Boost Stats
description: Increasing Mastery Rank will also boost Talent.

title: Increase Mastery Rank to Boost Stats
description:
Increase the Mastery Rank of 4★ characters that come
 with costumes to unlock color variants.

title: Purchasing Song Covers
description:
Some songs have cover versions sung
 by other characters.

title: Purchasing Song Covers
description:
Head to the Cover Shop to purchase
 cover versions of certain songs.

title: Purchasing Song Covers
description:
Increase Character Rank to obtain Cover Cards
 which can be traded in at the Cover Shop.

title: Title Display
description:
Titles have rarity and rank, and
 some may change in appearance depending on these.

title: Co-op Show Rewards (1)
description:
Rewards earned from Co-op
 Shows are greatly increased.

title: Obtaining Stamps
description:
Stamp Vouchers can be traded at the
 Stamp Shop for whichever Stamps you like.

title: Obtaining Stamp Vouchers
description:
Obtain Stamp Vouchers from events
 or by increasing Character Rank.

title: Virtual Show - Lobby (1)
description:
You can interact with other players
 in the Virtual Show Lobby.

title: Virtual Show - Lobby (2)
description:
Purchase Avatar Costumes, Accessories, and other
 items from the Virtual Shop in the Lobby.

title: Ver. Select
description:
You can change the song version by
 tapping on Ver. Select before starting a show.

title: Assigning Favorite Stamps
description:
Go to Favorite Stamp Settings to set
 which stickers you use most often.

title: Increasing Your Score (1)
description:
Increase a show's score
 by increasing your Talent.

title: Increasing Your Score (2)
description: Higher combos earn you bigger score boosts.

title: Obtaining Practice Scores
description:
Practice Scores that are used to level up
 your characters, are mainly obtained by completing shows.

title: Music Video Viewer
description:
Watch  3D music videos
in the Music Video Viewer.

title: Unlocking New Functions ①
description:
Reach Player Rank 5 to unlock
 the Challenge Show game mode.

title: Unlocking New Functions ③
description:
Reach Player Rank 30 to
 unlock the Skill Up function.

title: Auto-Play
description: During Auto-Play, the rhythm game will be played automatically.

title: Auto-Play
description: Auto-Play can be used up to 10 times per day.

title: Event Story
description:
You can view previously unlocked
 Event Stories from the Story menu.

title: Event Story
description:
View an event's final episode to
 unlock previously held After Show.

title: Challenge Shows - EX Levels
description:
Once a Challenge Show's Stage reaches 100,
it becomes an EX Level.

title: Challenge Shows - EX Levels
description:
You can earn Crystals every day by
increasing your Challenge Shows' EX Levels.

title: Friends
description:
You can send a friend request to another
 player from their profile or from a Co-op Show.

title: Purchasing Song Covers
description:
Cover Cards can be traded in
 at the Cover Card Exchange.

title: Hairstyle
description: Hairstyles that come with characters can be obtained when reaching Mastery Rank 2.

title: Hairstyle
description: You can select Hairstyles from Costumes.

title: Challenge Stamp
description: Get a stamp each time you Clear a Challenge Show.

title: Challenge Stamp
description: Select a special item as a reward from the Challenge Show Day 7's Challenge Stamp.

title: Dress-up Mode
description: By turning on Dress-up Mode in Costumes or the Costume Shop, you can dress Characters up in Costumes that you have not yet obtained including color variants.

title: Profile
description: Custom Profile allows you to design your own original profile.

title: Birthday Character
description: Birthday Characters are special Characters with the Birthday rarity.

title: Character Exchange
description: Trade for previously featured General Characters at the Character Exchange.

title: Event Bonus
description: Increasing Mastery Rank will also earn Event Bonuses.

title: Trust Rank
description: Increasing Trust Rank will earn special Titles and rewards between certain Characters.

title: Trust Rank
description: Playing shows will earn Trust EXP between the Leader and the other 4 Characters within the group.

title: Friends
description: You can invite Friends to a private room for Co-op Shows and Virtual Shows.

title: Auto-Play
description: In the Auto-Play settings, you can set your Bonus Energy to restore automatically and play Shows continuously.

title: Lessons from the Old Lady at the Hospital
